x-sap-shortText: API to access job requisition data such as job descriptions.

x-servers.description: OData APIs for the SuccessFactors Data Centers

info.title: Job Requisition
info.description:
Use these APIs to create and manage job requisitions, use Job Analyzer to improve job requisitions, as well as access information of qualified candidates.

 You can find your company's API server in [List of API Servers in SAP SuccessFactors.](https://help.sap.com/viewer/d599f15995d348a1b45ba5603e2aba9b/LATEST/en-US/af2b8d5437494b12be88fe374eba75b6.html)
